name: Michael.Jackson DAO
description:
Michael Jackson was a great artist. MichaelDAO is a DAO organization created in honor of Michael Jackson. Token name: Michael. In honor of Michael, we have a constant 5 billion tokens and the project owner does not hold tokens.

By supporting us, you will receive:

1. Each donor will receive the first limited edition Michael Jackson NFT at a ratio of 1ETH:1 after the fundraising ends. Each NFT will be unique.

2. Whitelist quota of Michael Jackson's NFT in the subsequent marketing campaign

3. Pledged tokens $ Michael gets a share of the project revenue

We have already contacted and made plans to list well-known exchanges and made a complete marketing plan.

Our goal: to reward everyone who loves Michael with a great deal of money.

More project dividends will be created for Michael's supporters in the future!
payDisclosure:
Thank you for supporting us. 
The spirit of Michael Jackson shines on the world.
